{"tid":1386210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翁靜晶：人間正道是「警黑勾結」","createTime":"2019-07-30T09:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:24:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ed6a6b14dd56e22adf398cde4c436a421ee046","tid":1386210,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"一群熱心市民就「定慧寺事件」於2017年9月拍片道出「警黑勾結」，僅兩年之後發生《逃犯條例》修例及連串事件，證明「正義女俠」翁靜晶甚有先見之明。<br />\n<br />\n當年定慧寺義工團隊出錢出力調查、搜證，再自行去法院起訴，免得斂財者就會繼續逍遙法外，繼續騙財。<br />\n<br />\n翁靜晶近日指出：「警察和相關執法部門，根本不會拘捕政權保護的 untouchables (不能惹的人) 。仍然在法網之外的，除了已『隱身』於大陸的艷尼釋智定，還有「提早退休」到英國的梁麗姚督察。貪腐的政府，包庇自己人，維護既得利益者，形成了一群惡勢的untouchables, 他們做任何壞事也不會面對法律責任，這是文明社會的悲哀。」<br />\n<br />\n翁靜晶是退休律師，她長期為正義執言：「一視同仁執法，是理所當然的，正所謂『天子犯法與庶民同罪，但選擇性執法，是不會長治久安的。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.modia.com.hk/2019/07/28/135746/%E7%BF%81%E9%9D%9C%E6%99%B6%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%96%93%E6%AD%A3%E9%81%93%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E8%AD%A6%E9%BB%91%E5%8B%BE%E7%B5%90%E3%80%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.modia.com.hk%2F2019%2F07%2F28%2F135746%2F%25E7%25BF%2581%25E9%259D%259C%25E6%2599%25B6%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%2598%25AF%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%258B%25BE%25E7%25B5%2590%25E3%2580%258D%2F&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCucWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=469b1980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.modia.com.hk/2019/07/28/135746/%E7%BF%81%E9%9D%9C%E6%99%B6%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%96%93%E6%AD%A3%E9%81%93%E6%98%AF%E3%80%8C%E8%AD%A6%E9%BB%91%E5%8B%BE%E7%B5%90%E3%80%8D/</a>"},{"pid":"7d68eef093ec9cf5a51a0c1d0c0fcb7134b5b705","tid":1386210,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"翁靜晶質疑林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n香港返送中局勢升級以來，林鄭取消了很多活動，但同中共中聯辦高官一同專程、高調去參加釋智慧的葬禮。林鄭舉動引起港人指責。<br />\n<br />\n香港前藝人、轉行當律師的翁靜晶7月24日在Facebook轉貼傳媒報道《【人命賤如草芥】元朗恐襲高官失蹤 林鄭722早上出席寶蓮寺追思會》。<br />\n<br />\n翁靜晶並在帖文中質疑，難怪7月22日下午3時的記者招待會，她不敢回答她早上那裏去了，「只要處理好正經事，您去那裏都可以，但當天香港正是水深火熱，您這樣的選擇，就是『親疏有別、輕重不分』」。<br />\n<br />\n翁靜晶還表示，「她當日是否在寶蓮寺享用完『精美齋菜』才回程市區。要不然，為甚麼搞到三點？」<br />\n<br />\n還有網友質疑林鄭月娥與釋智慧關係：「果然係朋友，大家都係殊途同歸，都係地獄見。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-07-30/30224123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2019-07-30%2F30224123&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCucWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=413316ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-07-30/30224123</a>"},{"pid":"5c6d4d765647b5aaf40d396b1a3806cb08c94c74","tid":1386210,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:37:09.000Z","msg":"［突發］機場要人！機場要人！機場要人！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386103</a>"},{"pid":"0dcf59678b4976a30eec6e6dff10aa2d2d79e2af","tid":1386210,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:43:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a611968bc6be8c92962aa649ed708ce1bf4844a5","tid":1386210,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-ort2-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/ac6262262f28c50928fadeacf32e0c91/5DD68B0C/t51.2885-15/e35/65802550_2308206292773208_9095015882905632440_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-ort2-1.cdninstagram.com\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-ort2-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2Fac6262262f28c50928fadeacf32e0c91%2F5DD68B0C%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F65802550_2308206292773208_9095015882905632440_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-ort2-1.cdninstagram.com&h=af031ab3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf85f850f469ba7ca6430749d7ed5f721057ca8c","tid":1386210,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}